{"tid":1305206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[知法犯法] 有警員出示警員證搭免費車","createTime":"2019-07-10T20:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T20:17:03.000Z","uid":204765,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"60c84cf787015311c20d186de50b9e48ec349d39","tid":1305206,"uid":204765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:15:31.000Z","msg":"「Facebook專頁「從事電影業嘅巴士佬」發帖，表示年中都有些警務人員上巴士時會出示警員委任證給車長，以便免費乘車。而巴士司機「為免卻不必要的麻煩」，很多都會隻眼開隻眼閉，默許警務人員搭順風車：<span style=\"color: red;\">感覺就好似潛規則</span>。<br />\n<br />\n據《警察通例》第6章「行為及紀律」第36條，「<span style=\"color: red;\">警務人員乘搭公共交通工具應繳付適當費用</span>，除非獲得警察總部豁免，並取得公務員事務局局長及保安局局長同意。在此情況下，警務人員必須穿著制服及正在當值。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2376600/巴士車長曝有警員出示警員證搭免費車%E3%80%80籲同業：別再接受非巴士公司發出證件?r=cpsdem\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2376600%2F%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E6%9B%9D%E6%9C%89%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%AD%89%E6%90%AD%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E8%BB%8A%25E3%2580%2580%E7%B1%B2%E5%90%8C%E6%A5%AD%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%A5%E5%86%8D%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E9%9D%9E%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%99%BC%E5%87%BA%E8%AD%89%E4%BB%B6%3Fr%3Dcpsdem&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnWLTbr5529Gqcy%2B2MeRGono%3D&h=ed8ebd26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2376600/巴士車長曝有警員出示警員證搭免費車%E3%80%80籲同業：別再接受非巴士公司發出證件?r=cpsdem</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港警察 知法犯法</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e24735ff10b7e2c74eb6243b4c37cc9bf6cba39","tid":1305206,"uid":144522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:17:03.000Z","msg":"佢地根本都唔撚知法"}]}